		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"WordPress 5.1“Betty”\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/02/22/betty/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:50:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2019/02/22/betty/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 21 Feb 2019 20:41:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"发布\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://cn.wordpress.org/?p=1197\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:91:\"WordPress 5.1简体中文版现已开放下载，或在您的WordPress仪表盘中升级。\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Jimmy Xu\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44214:\"\n<h2 style=\"text-align:center\">每天都好一点点</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.1/update.svg\" alt=\"\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress 5.1简体中文版现已<a href=\"https://cn.wordpress.org/download/\">开放下载</a>，或在您的WordPress仪表盘中升级。我们将此版本命名为“Betty”，以纪念爵士歌手贝蒂·卡特。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>继<a href=\"https://cn.wordpress.org/2018/12/10/bebo/\">WordPress 5.0</a>引入区块编辑器之后，5.1致力于细节，尤其着重提升编辑器的整体性能。此外，此次发布通过对于站点管理员和开发者来说必不可少的工具，为将来更好、更快、更安全的WordPress奠定了基石。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>站点健康</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.1/site-health.svg\" alt=\"\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>基于安全和速度的考虑，此次发布为您带来了WordPress的首个<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/01/14/php-site-health-mechanisms-in-5-1/\">站点健康</a>功能。WordPress会开始向仍在运行古旧PHP版本的站点管理员展示通知。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>在安装新插件时，WordPress的站点健康功能会检查插件是否需要与您的站点不兼容的PHP版本。如果是这样，WordPress会阻止您安装此插件。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<h2>编辑器性能</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.1/editor-performance.svg\" alt=\"\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>在WordPress 5.0中引入后，我们依然在不断改进新的区块编辑器。最重要的是，WordPress 5.1在编辑器内包含了可靠的性能改进。现在您应该能感觉到编辑器打开更快、键入文字更流畅。</p>\n\n\n\n<p>我们会在下个版本中加入更多的性能改进。</p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<h2>开发者的小确幸</h2>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/01/28/multisite-support-for-site-metadata-in-5-1/\">多站点元数据</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>5.1引入了新的数据库表来存储站点相关的元数据，及其他与多站点/网络相关的任意站点数据。</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/01/23/cron-api-changes-in-wordpress-5-1/\">Cron API</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Cron API已更新，包含全新函数来协助返回数据，和全新过滤器来修改cron存储。其他修改会影响cron在运行FastCGI和PHP-FPM版本7.0.16或更高的服务器上的运行。</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2018/05/16/preparing-wordpress-for-a-javascript-future-part-1-build-step-and-folder-reorganization/\">全新JS构建流程</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>WordPress 5.1在5.0版重构大量代码之后，包含了全新的JavaScript构建方式。</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2019/01/23/miscellaneous-developer-focused-changes-in-5-1/\">其他小确幸</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>其他改进包括：</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>更新<code>WP_DEBUG_LOG</code>常量的值</li><li>测试套件中新的测试文件配置常量，新的插件动作钩子</li><li><code>wp_unique_post_slug()</code>、<code>WP_User_Query</code>和<code>count_users()</code>的短路过滤器</li><li>新的<code>human_readable_duration</code>函数</li><li>改良的分类法metabox清理</li><li>使用<code>WP_Meta_Query</code>时有限的元数据键<code>LIKE</code>支持</li><li>注册REST API端点时全新的“不能这样使用”通知</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>…以及更多！</p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\" />\n\n\n\n<h2>开发团队</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>此次发布由<a href=\"http://ma.tt/\">Matt Mullenweg</a>领头，<a href=\"https://pento.net/\">Gary Pendergast</a>担任<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/changeset/42343\">资深代码重构师</a>及<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/changeset/43309\">诗人</a>。他们得到了以下个人的帮助。这次发布包含了561人的贡献，其中更有231人是首次做出贡献。在您喜欢的音乐服务中听听贝蒂·卡特，并看看下面这些个人资料吧：<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/0x6f0/\">0x6f0</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1265578519-1/\">1265578519</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/1naveengiri/\">1naveengiri</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/360zen/\">360zen</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aardrian/\">aardrian</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jorbin/\">Aaron Jorbin</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abdullahramzan/\">Abdullah Ramzan</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abhayvishwakarma/\">Abhay Vishwakarma</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abhijitrakas/\">Abhijit Rakas</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ibachal/\">Achal Jain</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/achbed/\">achbed</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/adamsilverstein/\">Adam Silverstein</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ajitbohra/\">Ajit Bohra</a>、<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/schlessera/\">Alain Sc